    • Constructor Detail

      • FilterRegistry

        public FilterRegistry()
        Constructs a new FilterRegistry. This will register the following Filters by default:
        • ConstraintFilter
        • CooldownFilter
        • DirectMessageFilter
        • PermissionsFilter
        • UserMuteFilter

        position - the FilterPosition at which the Filter gets registered
